{"id":181055,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/村民报警被扣和谐奖奖金/","date":"2011-09-23T10:30:02Z","modified":"2011-09-23T10:30:02Z","title":"村民报警被扣&#8221;和谐奖&#8221;奖金","content":"<p>Magicloud 写道 &#8220;中广网北京9月23日消息 据中国之声《央广新闻》报道，北京顺义区一位村民最近遭遇了一件让人想不通的事情，因为家中被盗报警，村里竟然怪他没看好门，扣除了他当月的“和谐奖”奖金。这件事情引来了网友的围观。顺义区后沙峪镇宣传部工作人员称，扣除“和谐奖”并非强压村民报警，而是一种激励村民提高防范的措施。由于该村流动人口多，治安环境较复杂，经常出现偷抢等案件。为了加强管理，村委会实施了这个办法。据称，一年来，村民报案的数量大大下降。在设立“和谐奖”之前平均每月有50起左右的报警，设立之后每月报警数不足10起。&#8221;<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/18cf39f4/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%A5%E8%AD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%A3%22%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E5%A5%96%22%E5%A5%96%E9%87%91&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F09%2F23%2F0818211%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%A5%E8%AD%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%A3%22%E5%92%8C%E8%B0%90%E5%A5%96%22%E5%A5%96%E9%87%91&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fsociety.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F09%2F23%2F0818211%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/114252047292/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/18cf39f4/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/114252047292/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/18cf39f4/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=tCtsu2hniDA:AUw-Midyw5M:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=tCtsu2hniDA:AUw-Midyw5M:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border